    "steam_appid": 1831400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831400/extras/fbb6f20a02257464fd9171201619ad5c.avif?t=1770898589\" width=800 height=364 /></span><i>Build, defend your sanctum, gather resources and survive in this post apocalyptic simulated survival game.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Plot </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Just as you finally find a means to survive, you are enveloped by the events of the disasters and city's champions and villains' destructive conflicts threatening your very presence. Join the descendants of the dogmatic in defense of the local area against wicked and the vile. This may take much more than you might think, both within and outside your sanctum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your sanctum from scratch, start with little water and other resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gather resources, run scouting and otherwise expeditions to nearing zones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build, upgrade your shelter, house migrating survivors of the disasters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build an inventory, upgrade and enhance your population</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Select one of 4 paragon types, bringing bonuses to your settlement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > House select paragons to further upgrade your settlement and enhance your population for further success</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Perform and defend raids in simulated single-player environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Perform other encounters and trade with nearing settlements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defend and dominate against ai world settlements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play through a refined story that composes your own settlement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gather inventory from relic hunts, equip your settlers with them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Skirmish through your best settlement possible by the 100th day.</p></li></ul>",
